article.headline: Robinson scores 16, Little Rock knocks off Tennessee Tech 81-43
article.description: — Khalen Robinson had 16 points in Little Rock's 81-43 victory over Tennessee Tech on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Robinson scores 16, Little Rock knocks off Tennessee Tech 81-43
article.story: LITTLE ROCK, Ark. -- — Khalen Robinson had 16 points in Little Rock's 81-43 victory over Tennessee Tech on Saturday night. Robinson shot 6 for 9 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 3 of 3 from the free throw line for the Trojans (20-11, 14-4 Ohio Valley Conference). Makhel Mitchell scored 14 points while shooting 4 of 7 from the field and 6 for 8 from the line, and added seven rebounds and six assists. Jaylen Crocker-Johnson had 12 points and finished 5 of 10 from the field. The Trojans picked up their ninth straight victory. Kyle Layton finished with 14 points and two steals for the Golden Eagles (10-21, 5-13). Josiah Davis added 13 points for Tennessee Tech. Daniel Egbuniwe also had 11 points, two steals and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
